        ul.margin-extra.without_margin.blue-list.font-blue
          li
            a href="http://www.revenuearchitects.com/services/revenue-strategy/" - Revenue Strategy
          li
            a href="http://www.revenuearchitects.com/services/revenue-systems/" - Revenue Systems
          li
            a href="http://www.revenuearchitects.com/services/revenue-programs/" - Revenue Programs
        p.margin-extra.without_margin After completing the Revenue Grader, teams can quickly identify priorities. Priorities can range widely - from developing market segmentation and crafting better value propositions to deploying marketing automation, closed loop marketing programs and enhancing account based marketing and sales.


      .span4.center-image
        a href="http://revenuearchitects.com/resources/revenue-architecture/"
